The unique proprietary identifier assigned to each Building Permit entity.

This field represents an ATTOM DATA Unique identifier assigned to the property during it's entire life in our databases. Regardless if the records is a future record, active, or inactive property. For commercial properties or attached residentail properties, it's possible to find several different buildingpermitId's  to one attomid and vice versa.
